name: PlaneSpotter
0: ”Alexa, ask plane spotter to tell me the closest plane to me”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: plane spotter
des:
Plane Spotter uses the ADS-B service to inform you of the closest plane to you or any location you choose and tells you a bit about the plane!

You can ask Plane Spotter:
- Alexa, open plane spotter
- Alexa, ask plane spotter to find the closest plane to me
- Alexa, ask plane spotter to find the closest plane to 1 Rocket Road, Hawthorne, California
- Alexa, ask plane spotter to find the nearest plane to me
- ...and more!
